{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's some physical damage in my eye, but I-- I-- I-- I saved my eye.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And possibly, because I wore glasses, that-- that saved, because my face was totally burned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was, like, raw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was my-- not my problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My problem was that I was accused of being-- of having sabotaged, of sabotaging the plant, because I put about two bays out of commission.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Like a bay-- there was a big, long bay where they had dozens of pieces of equipment and machinery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And everything just went to a standstill, till they reset.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had to check what-- what happened before they reset the breaker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It must have been a half an hour or an hour that they lost, so they accused me of sabotaging.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was interesting that the-- the-- the civilian boss that I worked for came to bat for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said he-- he said that it was an accident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And instead of putting me back into work with the tools, he put me into a warehouse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I became the warehouse keeper, which was, again, a very fortuitous-- fortuitous occurrence for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My-- my face healed-- didn't leave a mark on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the-- my eye came-- my-- my sight came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I worked in the-- in the-- in this plant and in this warehouse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I started manufacturing little heaters, which I proceeded to sell to the German civilians in the factory that worked with us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You see, all these-- we were-- the-- the prisoners were working with civilians, side-by-side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my father was working on a-- on a lathe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And-- and I-- and his boss was a very kind, old German gentleman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he kept telling my father what the news were from the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
